                </ul>
                <div class="mt-4 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-3">
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-xs italic">
                    The Purāṇas identify Hiraṇyagarbha with Brahma — the first
                    conscious being who embodied the Light of Knowledge that
                    illuminates all existence.
                  </p>
